Last night our tank left and we had no melees in the group to tank in PoV. So I suggested that we just ping pong kite golems as we wait. The exp ended up being better then what a conventional group would get, and we decided to just get another nuker instead of a tank. Ench, necro, cleric, wiz, wiz, wiz.<br>
<br>
